Text: Omg yes. I put on my resting bitch face and purchase my Apple cider vinegar and cigarettes. Feels weird though

Author: novakayne96
Text: Super. I make two grocery trips. One for everything my family will eat. And another for just me. I've gotten weird looks from cashiers, since it's always an inane amount of vegetables, diet drinks, and and ice cream. Like let me pretend this is just a few days of vegan "normal person" eating and not enough to last me a whole damn week.
